        <item>
            <title>1.7.6</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 18:54:46 -0600</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>28</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.7.6</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Version 1.7.6 — Smarter Illustrations</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>New:</strong> Each story detail — character, setting, action, mood — is now sent as a separate concept to the image engine for sharper, more faithful illustrations</li>
  <li><strong>New:</strong> If an image fails to generate, StoryFox progressively simplifies the prompt while keeping the main character intact</li>
  <li><strong>Improved:</strong> Better breed-specific rendering for dog and cat characters</li>
</ul>]]></description>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
